<i>Ciccaba nigrolineata</i> (Sclater, 1859)
The <b>Black-and-white Owl</b> (<i>Strix nigrolineata</i>) is a species of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Owl" title="Owl">owl</a> in the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strigidae" title="Strigidae" class="mw-redirect">Strigidae</a> family.<sup id="cite_ref-IUCN2012_1-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-IUCN2012-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-ITIS_2-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-ITIS-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup> It is found in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Belize" title="Belize">Belize</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Colombia" title="Colombia">Colombia</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Costa_Rica" title="Costa Rica">Costa Rica</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ecuador" title="Ecuador">Ecuador</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/El_Salvador" title="El Salvador">El Salvador</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guatemala" title="Guatemala">Guatemala</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Honduras" title="Honduras">Honduras</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mexico" title="Mexico">Mexico</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicaragua" title="Nicaragua">Nicaragua</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Panama" title="Panama">Panama</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peru" title="Peru">Peru</a>, and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Venezuela" title="Venezuela">Venezuela</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-IUCN2012_1-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-IUCN2012-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup>
Its natural <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Habitat" title="Habitat">habitats</a> are subtropical or tropical dry <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Forest" title="Forest">forests</a>, subtropical or tropical moist lowland forests, and subtropical or tropical moist <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Montane_forest" title="Montane forest" class="mw-redirect">montane forests</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-IUCN2012_1-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-IUCN2012-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup>
